As of Saturday, Mass. has received 1,516,600 doses of #vaccine, of which 1,082,785, or 71.4%, has been administered. DPH reported an additional 1,949 confirmed #COVID19 cases today, bringing the statewide total to 527,435 since the start of the pandemic.
